				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load up CTY_Main_A\r\nOpen Recon, and turn on Roll Amazing\r\nteleport to -269; 6; -149, and a dialog will auto-start\r\nChose the deception option in the dialog\r\nAfter succeeding, the dialog should soon end\r\nwalk up to and click on S_LOW_BaneiteOfficer02_de084b09-99c6-426e-9159-f692d180d418 to initiate this dialog."
